Subject: RE: Static IP has been assigned IP should be pining but not able to open in GUI
Description:
Dear Team,

we have not able to login via GUI, but the IP are pinging, we are facing issue to onboard the server, please try to resolve the issue.

Regards,
sai
What_We_Know__c:
managed to investigate the issue, and the cause was that the certificates could not be loaded by the nginx configuration and therefor it couldn't go through.
After I reimported the CA's and applied them to the server, the UI could be successfully open.
Next_Steps__c: have a remote session and investigate
Solution_Comment__c:
managed to investigate the issue, and the cause was that the certificates could not be loaded by the nginx configuration and therefor it couldn't go through.
